snippet.title: Medal of Honor: Frontline PS3 Trailer
snippet.description: Exclusive to the PlayStation 3 version of the new Medal of Honor is an HD remake of the classic Medal of Honor: Frontline. This trailer puts epic moments from the new and the old side by side, showing you just how much the franchise has evolved over the past 8 years.
